Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does Chimera look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is eating, but I still think\Nshe's under the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should take her to the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably just ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Rikka was feeding her lots\Nfor what she called "Project Super-Size."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. So, where is Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise, Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time of awakening is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light! The Light Beings are\Nroasting me alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, give me darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roast to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi, morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of the second term.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were leaving for school...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:40.62,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Superior Contract...\Nof Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she ran off by herself\Nsaying she was going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buongiorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao! How was your long vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to get a little weird\Nevery time there's a new term.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in second term!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about you, Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer is as funny as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I only have eyes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Really, who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have eyes for you, Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am devoted to you, Kumin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An exchange student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? She wasn't like this before\Nsummer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably shrank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stare longingly after \NRikka without saying a word to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,each other right after summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your love cool off in the hot summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! If you wanna know,\Nit's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposite? Do you mean,\Nyou spent the entire summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you defile my master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Where did you come from anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in this press corps?\NAnd you're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. There's no need to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Statistically speaking, the second year\Nof high school is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-i-is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what the statistics say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to discuss \Nit! Anyway, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that Rikka's been \Nacting off all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't treat my master cruelly, I trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you talk with Shichimiya\Nin an overly friendly way again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! I know I'm dense,\Nbut I know better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Rikka practically goes over\Nto visit her every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've really hit it off since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka! Hey, Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi wants to whisper \Nsweet nothings to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you mean. She is a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, anyone would wanna run from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow to smithereens, fruitful offline life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Wicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is in the most pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she mention anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always comes with me on my angel hunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's helping out since I helped revive\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was thinking of entering\Na Superior Contract with Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superior Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Now that the Dark Flame Dragon\Nhas been revived,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she thinks it's necessary \Nas a contract holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superior Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:06:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If memory serves me, those two\Nare bound by a Lover's Contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Superior Contract would have to mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-why are you turning red?!\NGet your mind out of the gutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! You're the \None who's turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a dirty mind for a freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you were imagining Takanashi\Ntaking off her clothes and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it! Don't say it! Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow!\NDon't say it! Don't say it! Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She meant kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting the same as earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KISSING, HOW BOYS FEEL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, just seeing if you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to come along, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we have girl talk to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the famous Faerie Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any type of spirit may live here. Caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not planning to butt in\Nwhere you're not wanted again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe! C'mon, Takanashi. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there any particular reason\Nwe needed to come to a bath house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Togashi can't interfere\Nand Takanashi can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus there are no weapons to attack with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I didn't factor in\Nthat this idiot might come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko, come over here. They have funny baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it's a sonic training area!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you must come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my meditation is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this works. Now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.91,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MIKAN\NSoak away the daily fatigue\Nin our four seasons bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in deep concentration\Nto prepare for the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inevitable?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Superior Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani, are you reading my thoughts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Morisummer miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danger! Break away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will join this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itty bitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some, Mjolnir Hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. When the Dark Flame Dragon\Nwas brought back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my part of the Contract \Nbecame more solidified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He restricts my activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solve this correctly, and you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he believes that I will obey\Nif he rewards me with something black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is heavy-handed with me\Nin spite of my contractual status.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably thinks that saying\N"dark" will please me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Master has gone wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you want to enter\Na Superior Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Otherwise it will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Dark Flame Dragon has been revived,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe Contract must be revised accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I think about it,\Nthe more I feel I might dissolve away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to watch me \Nto make sure I don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is in love with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Remember how\NI had a lifeguard job at the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it happened.\NIt's someone named Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! I'm not bragging about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm devoted to Kumin-senpai all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I worked\Nall through summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I could buy her a present. But for what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chihiro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto, I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, Chihiro is a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto, we must be joined by\Nthe Red Thread of Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to run into each other in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just stop. I am... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:25.10,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki, I wish you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't find out anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This one time,\NTakanashi was very tight lipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd tell you herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She wants you to \Ncome here after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.60,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BASE\NCOME HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to go. She looked serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing for me. \NIt was almost too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just thinking how much\Nyou really love us, Morisummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, that's crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mjolnir Hammer, it's almost time.\NWe have to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time, Master. Godspeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I can't go through with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan, you asked us\Nto make sure you didn't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many other\Nhigher contract categories
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Wicked Lord Shingan's\Nselection of Lover's Contracts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a diverse variety...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan is all-powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you've always done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You conquered your fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Met Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dove into his arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And entered into a binding contract with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all this because\NWicked Lord Shingan is all-powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it this far because of\NWicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan really is all-powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The emotions have such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you all the power I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop taking so long! \NTogashi will arrive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fully aware of that \Nwithout your information!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan, it is\Nall the natural logic of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up? Did you make a new discovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuta Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, Dark Flame Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, Ghelzonianses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick one and stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I command you to enter into a \NSuperior Lover's Contract with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,myself and Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superior Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot determine its significance,\Nthen you are a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't mean... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My demands have been stated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hows and whys of the world\Nmean nothing to the Wicked Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you or will you not? Choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. I didn't mean to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold my shoulders so I can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I was momentarily possessed\Nby something dark, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you, \Nbut it's so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel so scared and embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too scared. Why am I so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to force ourselves to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am bound to you for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am bound to you by contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why Sophia entrusted \Neverything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must consummate the emotion\Nshe entrusted to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I thought I \Nknew how hopeless I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm worse at it than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really thought it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, remember how you told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would spend fun time together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that nothing could make you happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live in the same apartment,\Ngo to school together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...go home together, eat together....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...play video games together,\Nget mad, and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could feel like such a drag,\Nand then feel like such a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of those things is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than any hugs and kisses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nor other things that lovers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me happy, and it makes me\Nfeel very close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, you will always \Nbe the only one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, Yuta, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it is gradually changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do stuff like this a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning it was pinkies.\NNext we held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening slowly, but it is changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HOME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Chimera did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come home quick, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, our family is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Chimera Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Two," nothing. There are six of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six! A chimaeric beast army!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to let it \Nend like this, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you mad at me? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it! I practically raised you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least you could do\Nis to let us watch you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Watch you do it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not make it sound so vulgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting away! Hold it right there, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will become of Rikka's chunibyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will become of our love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rikka and I have always\Nheld on to one thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one thought from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one thought we will always hold on to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:05.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"EVEN THOUGH I'M IN CHUNIBYO,\NI STILL WANT LOVE!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE END
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,